Obstinacy	#606.	 obduracy, obduration
Malevolence	#907.	 gall, venom, rancor, rankling, virulence, mordacity, acerbity churlishness &c. (discourtesy). hardness of heart, heart of stone, obduracy
Impenitence	#951.	 lack of contrition. hardness of heart, seared conscience, induration, obduracy. V. be impenitent &c. adj.
